        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Prosperous outlook in Texas.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Brassos </placeName><date when="1823-04-24">24 April 1823</date></p>

<p>Dr. Sir</p>

<p>I have applied to the <persName>Governor </persName>for a grant for my <persName>Brothers eldest
son</persName> and requested him to hand you the papers please use your
influence in geting it completed the <persName>settlers </persName>are perfectly satisfied
and determined to stick many of them have butter cheese and milk
and fat cattle in abundance and fine prospects for good crops on
Both <placeName>rivers </placeName>I intended writing you a long letter but refer you to your
<persName>Brother </persName>he can tell you maiby what has been saved out of the general
reck the <persName>inhabitants </persName>wish to see you very much</p>

<p><persName>L Hawkins</persName></p>

<p>[Addressed:]  <persName> Judge S F Austin</persName>   <placeName>Bexar P. Texas</placeName>.</p>

        </div1>
